ix for code scanning alert no. 512: Insecure randomness","Fix deselecting fields in joins with inactive implicitly joined remapped columns","docs - relative links","docs - fix markdown links in Debian installation guide","feat(sdk): Fix and improve Metabot for SDK","Fix: UXW-204 don't show upsells to non-admins on paid plans","update jspdf to 3.0.2","Auto-update documentation for release-x.56.x","Navigating Settings Presents Error When you Select Auth or Embedding Sections","docs - note on pinning","Add documentation for password settings on Metabase Cloud","docs - clarify JWT Identity Provider URI instructions","Manual backport of preserving table whitespaces changes","Postgres queries fail with `java.lang.Class.isArray()` errors after upgrade to v0.56.3","A caret cursor is not visible in filter inputs","Content layout shift when checking an item in a collection","Pivot table export outputs blank values when pivoting on integer columns","Auto-update documentation for release-x.56.x","Better branch detection if relevant files are changed for CI","Fix flaky UpdatesNavItem test","Update Debian/systemd docs","Fix references to pre-56 Troubleshooting admin menu","Drill through no longer works for pivot tables in the latest version","Fix flaky test for metabase-browser custom element","Card filters seem to be avoiding the linkage to dashboard filters","Discard cached field values will... refresh the values?","Fix tabs alignment for horizontal tabs with grow (#61895)","docs: translations limitations","skip flaky loki row chart tests","There are more selected columns than there are total columns","refactor(sdk): Rename embedding-sdk directory to embedding-sdk-bundle","chore: upgrade vulnerable cipher-base package","chore: upgrade vulnerable sha.js package","[BOT-316] Metabase BE support for dynamic agent profiles","Respond with HTTP status 500 when Store API request fails during Cloud migration","fix(sdk): Add background-light to derived colors for the new embed","Content 